Deep learning, as with many other topics within data science, involves many skills, tools, languages, frameworks, and more.

The ODSC Deep Learning Guide is our compendium of 20 free resources for you to get started with deep learning, including videos from past ODSC deep learning presentations, tutorials, articles, and more.

This downloadable package includes 10 ODSC talks on deep learning, and 10 blogs on deep learning.  We also include insights from DL experts on how to get started with DL, mistakes to avoid, and hopes for the near future.

**Topics include:**
  * Saliency Maps
  * Reinforcement Learning
  * TensorLayer
  * Face Detectors
  * Keras
  * Convolutional Neural Networks
  * PyTorch
  * Kafka
  * Model Evaluation
  * Text Classification
  * Recommender Systems
